# Why This Works

Suppose

Original path

```
7 → 5 → 3 → Station
```

Reverse every edge

```
Station → 3 → 5 → 7
```

If reverse BFS reaches

```
7
```

then

```
7
```

can definitely send a signal to the station.

This is exactly the graph transpose idea.

